Adding new features to Project/Task Module:
- In Task list ( list view style):
  + Adding fields: Start Date, End Date
  + Remove field: Working time progress
  + Define new field: Completed Revenue
- Add new custom filter: Running Date - RD ( with 2 value From date, To Date)
- Terms:
  + Revenue per day of Task - RpD: Total Revenue/ (End date - Start date + 1)
  + Days of Task in duration: number of days of Task running in a specific period
- Completed Revenue (CR)
  + Without filter of RD: CR = RpD * (Current date - Start date + 1)
  + With filter of RD: CR = RpD * Days of Task in Duration of RD
       
